The paper deals with the extraction of structured data from unstructured web pages, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB). The approach also involves using machine learning techniques to automatically extract information, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
